{"tid":1863261,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"渣打前線缺防護 或按章工作","createTime":"2020-02-05T05:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T12:32:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"29727cc3a6a70f110384d89f8552e5c1b5b69d71","tid":1863261,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T05:22:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200205/WAV5JYIIZ6GQ5FILZXR2GFQSHI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200205%2FWAV5JYIIZ6GQ5FILZXR2GFQSHI%2F&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcT%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=44deda4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200205%2FWAV5JYIIZ6GQ5FILZXR2GFQSHI%2F&h=8d07c9d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200205/WAV5JYIIZ6GQ5FILZXR2GFQSHI/</a><br />\n<br />\n渣打前線缺防護 或按章工作<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200205/large/1580834201_0c7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200205%2Flarge%2F1580834201_0c7d.jpg&h=5f97ecbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n渣打香港目前分行運作正常。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】近日網傳渣打香港前線員工向公司提出七宗罪及五大訴求，包括要求提供合規格外科口罩，否則明日前按章工作及發起工業行動，預計首日行動會有600名員工參與。據了解，渣打香港目前分行運作正常。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：賀一誠封賭場半月 「買晒葡國口罩」<br />\n<br />\n要求提供口罩及加強消毒<br />\n<br />\n有自稱是渣打的員工，連日指控渣打防禦措施不足，呼籲除非渣打向前線員工提供合規格外科口罩、分行加強消毒及嚴格執行14天隔離等，否則會於2月6日前按章工作，預計首日行動會有600名同事參與。<br />\n<br />\n渣打香港發言人回應傳聞指，銀行因應武漢肺炎疫情已採取一系列措施，包括安排非緊急或必要服務員工盡量留在家中工作、以電話或視像會議取代面對面會議等。若員工或其家庭成員曾到訪內地，需留在家自我隔離14天，如員工因此未能上班，不會計算入其年假內。<br />\n<br />\n此外，渣打香港發言人表示，銀行會為前線員工量度體溫，並且提供三層式口罩及酒精搓手液，員工需要佩戴口罩上班。銀行亦都已經暫停部份分行服務，並且在持續營運的分行加強清潔消毒，亦在部份分行加裝屏障，減少員工與客戶的直接接觸。銀行會繼續檢視各項工作措施，作適當安排以保障員工。"},{"pid":"422f2f081979ce7419c0308cd307ee36f2991f9c","tid":1863261,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T05:34:29.000Z","msg":"醫護冇口罩都唔罷工啦<br />\n做銀行驚閪"},{"pid":"51ace1cb5bcbe238f5cb871a2453612fb413b6e0","tid":1863261,"uid":10274,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T05:58:16.000Z","msg":"渣打前線已經有5日假放<br />\n都仲唔滿足<br />\n難為我呢啲賣衫撚屌 仲要日日返工對客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2010a695373d3e3b07a7e687866a8433ca2421","tid":1863261,"uid":57490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T09:28:40.000Z","msg":"渣打都唔當員工係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f29634d7735860703b477ee5f2cf5f0e8e63964","tid":1863261,"uid":253809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:24:52.000Z","msg":"之前睇now 話有比員工放假wor, 係咪有人亂放流料?"},{"pid":"12c09e93e2fc28c7a2a4efbe2523cf12b74671e0","tid":1863261,"uid":161579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係老人區返工真係好驚"},{"pid":"626c024ea87f9963d07804b08182114f8b56496a","tid":1863261,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T12:32:45.000Z","msg":"冇口罩都只係按章？"}]}